column2: This property is not owned by a celebrity
column3: It was rented by a celeb 15 years ago and people show up expecting to see her. Sorry, 15 years too late!
It is a house with a roof and some bushes outside. It does have an interesting driveway, though. I don't know why I drove by it.
It didn't quite live up to everything I had heard. Maybe not their fault, the expectactions that people had built up for me were a bit unfair.
